data.description: Looking for great quality of life? Come to Lever Creek and experience tranquility and life near the lake with this 1.5 story home. Don't miss out on this beautiful, quaint community which offers close proximity to excellent heath care, education, and a wealth of recreational activities near Lake Murray. This 4 BR 3 BA home offers double ovens, gas cooktop, and gorgeous granite countertops. The master suite is on the main level with a huge walk in closet and master bath with granite countertops. Two additional bedrooms with vaulted ceilings and full bath are all on the main floor. Upstairs features a large bonus room with full bath. Covered Rear Porch, great for entertaining! This is an exciting time for Chapin, it's a wonderful place to call home.
